text: Nice elevator intro to a great theme for this series newcomer. I've been playing this game a lot with a friend when I come over and it cements Street Fighter being my favorite fighting game franchise. I absolutely love it, I really find the gameplay close to perfect. It is quite bare bones for now, but I'm sure we will be getting DLC packs to expand on the game. I've been listening to this particular theme quite a lot lately, it's composed by Ace Combat/Tekken/Ridge Racer veteran Kobayashi, it's nice to see him collaborate on a SF.
